Title: Heart Break
Plot: A strange case for Gibbs and his team opens when a Navy Commendar dies after successful surgery. While researching through commander's past, the team finds out that he collected a lot of enemies lately and tracks down a ensign making him the prime suspect. Soon Abby realizes that they got the wrong man...
GuestStars: Jessica Steen, Stacy Edwards, Nathan Wetherington, Michael Dempsey, Brian Dietzen, Billy Brown, Charles Walker, Derrex Brady, Tyler Kain
